<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TotalComp MX - Reporte Comparativo</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset & Base */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @page {
            {{if eq (len .Packages) 1}}
            size: A4 portrait;
            margin: 15mm;
            {{else}}
            size: A4 landscape;
            margin: 10mm;
            {{end}}
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #1e293b;
            background: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Watermark */
        body::before {
            content: 'TotalComp MX';
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
            font-size: 120pt;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.03);
            z-index: -1;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #10b981;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .date {
            font-size: 8pt;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Comparison Grid */
        .comparison-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .comparison-grid.single-mode {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .comparison-grid.comparison-mode {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }

        /* Package Card */
        .package-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        .comparison-grid.single-mode .package-card {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .package-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
        }

        .package-name {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .package-regime {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            color: #64748b;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Key Metrics */
        .key-metrics {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .metric {
            background: white;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .metric-label {
            font-size: 7pt;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .metric-value {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .metric.primary {
            border-left-color: #2563eb;
        }

        .metric.primary .metric-value {
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        .metric.success {
            border-left-color: #10b981;
        }

        .metric.success .metric-value {
            color: #059669;
        }

        .metric.premium {
            border-left-color: #8b5cf6;
        }

        .metric.premium .metric-value {
            color: #7c3aed;
        }

        /* Section */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            padding-left: 6px;
            border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
        }

        /* Items List */
        .items-list {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        .item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3px 6px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .item-label {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            color: #475569;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .item-value {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .item-value.positive {
            color: #059669;
        }

        .item-value.negative {
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .item-value.neutral {
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .item.total {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border-top: 2px solid #10b981;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #10b981;
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .item.total .item-label {
            color: #0f172a;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .item.total .item-value {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* Detail Badge */
        .detail-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 7pt;
            color: #64748b;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-left: 4px;
        }

        /* Tax Free Badge */
        .tax-free-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 7pt;
            color: #059669;
            background: #d1fae5;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-left: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Empty State */
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 9pt;
            font-style: italic;
            padding: 12px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-top: 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .legal-notice {
            font-size: 6pt;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .footer-brand {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 6.5pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Print Optimization */
        @media print {
            body {
                print-color-adjust: exact;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">TotalComp MX</div>
        <div class="date">{{.Date}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="title">
        {{if eq (len .Packages) 1}}
        Reporte de Compensaci√≥n 2025
        {{else}}
        Comparaci√≥n de Paquetes de Compensaci√≥n 2025
        {{end}}
    </div>

    <!-- Comparison Grid -->
    <div class="comparison-grid {{if eq (len .Packages) 1}}single-mode{{else}}comparison-mode{{end}}">
        {{range $idx, $pkg := .Packages}}
        <div class="package-card">
            <!-- Package Header -->
            <div class="package-header">
                <div class="package-name">{{$pkg.Name}}</div>
                <div class="package-regime">
                    {{if eq $pkg.Input.Regime "resico"}}RESICO{{else}}Sueldos y Salarios{{end}}
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Key Metrics -->
            <div class="key-metrics">
                <div class="metric primary">
                    <div class="metric-label">üí∞ Neto Mensual</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.NetSalary 2}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric success">
                    <div class="metric-label">üìÖ Neto Anual</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.YearlyNet 2}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric premium">
                    <div class="metric-label">‚ú® Neto Mensual Ajustado</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.MonthlyAdjusted 2}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Explanation -->
            <div style="background: #eff6ff; border-left: 2px solid #3b82f6; padding: 4px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px;">
                <p style="font-size: 6.5pt; color: #1e40af; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0;">
                    üí° <strong>Neto Mensual Ajustado:</strong> Incluye prestaciones anuales prorrateadas. Mejor m√©trica para comparar.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Monthly Breakdown -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">üí∞ Desglose Mensual</div>
                <div class="items-list">
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">Salario Bruto</div>
                        <div class="item-value neutral">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.GrossSalary 2}}</div>
                    </div>

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.ISRTax 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            (-) ISR
                            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.GrossSalary 0.0}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">{{formatFloat (div (mul $pkg.Calculation.ISRTax 100.0) $pkg.Calculation.GrossSalary) 2}}%</span>
                            {{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value negative">-${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.ISRTax 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.SubsidioEmpleo 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">(+) Subsidio al Empleo</div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">+${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.SubsidioEmpleo 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.IMSSWorker 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">(-) IMSS Trabajador</div>
                        <div class="item-value negative">-${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.IMSSWorker 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.FondoAhorroEmployee 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            (-) Fondo de Ahorro
                            {{if ne $pkg.Input.FondoAhorroPercent ""}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">{{$pkg.Input.FondoAhorroPercent}}%</span>
                            {{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value negative">-${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.FondoAhorroEmployee 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.ValesDespensaMonthly 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">(+) Vales de Despensa</div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">+${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.ValesDespensaMonthly 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.UnpaidVacationLoss 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            (-) Vacaciones no pagadas
                            {{if ne $pkg.Input.UnpaidVacationDays ""}}{{if ne $pkg.Input.UnpaidVacationDays "0"}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">{{$pkg.Input.UnpaidVacationDays}} d√≠as</span>
                            {{end}}{{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value negative">-${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.UnpaidVacationLoss 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{range $pkg.Calculation.OtherBenefits}}
                    {{if eq .Cadence "monthly"}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            (+) {{.Name}}
                            {{if .TaxFree}}<span class="tax-free-badge">Libre ISR</span>{{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">+${{formatFloat .Net 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}
                    {{end}}

                    <div class="item total">
                        <div class="item-label">= Neto Mensual</div>
                        <div class="item-value">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.NetSalary 2}}</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="item" style="background: #d1fae5; border-top: 2px solid #059669; border-bottom: 2px solid #059669; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 700;">
                        <div class="item-label" style="color: #065f46; font-weight: 700;">‚ú® Neto Mensual Ajustado</div>
                        <div class="item-value" style="color: #059669; font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700;">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.MonthlyAdjusted 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Annual Benefits -->
            {{$hasAnnualBenefits := false}}
            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.AguinaldoNet 0.0}}{{$hasAnnualBenefits = true}}{{end}}
            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.PrimaVacacionalNet 0.0}}{{$hasAnnualBenefits = true}}{{end}}
            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.FondoAhorroYearly 0.0}}{{$hasAnnualBenefits = true}}{{end}}
            {{range $pkg.Calculation.OtherBenefits}}{{if eq .Cadence "annual"}}{{$hasAnnualBenefits = true}}{{end}}{{end}}

            {{if $hasAnnualBenefits}}
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">üéÅ Prestaciones Anuales</div>
                <div class="items-list">
                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.AguinaldoNet 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            üéÑ Aguinaldo
                            {{if ne $pkg.Input.AguinaldoDays ""}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">{{$pkg.Input.AguinaldoDays}} d√≠as</span>
                            {{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.AguinaldoNet 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.PrimaVacacionalNet 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            üèñÔ∏è Prima Vacacional
                            {{if and (ne $pkg.Input.VacationDays "") (ne $pkg.Input.PrimaVacacionalPercent "")}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">{{$pkg.Input.VacationDays}} d√≠as @ {{$pkg.Input.PrimaVacacionalPercent}}%</span>
                            {{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.PrimaVacacionalNet 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.FondoAhorroYearly 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">üí∞ Fondo de Ahorro <span class="detail-badge">retorno 2x</span></div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">${{formatFloat $pkg.Calculation.FondoAhorroYearly 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{range $pkg.Calculation.OtherBenefits}}
                    {{if eq .Cadence "annual"}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            ‚ú® {{.Name}}
                            {{if .TaxFree}}<span class="tax-free-badge">Libre ISR</span>{{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value positive">${{formatFloat .Net 2}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}
                    {{end}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{end}}

            <!-- Employer Contributions -->
            {{$hasEmployerContributions := false}}
            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.InfonavitEmployerMonthly 0.0}}{{$hasEmployerContributions = true}}{{end}}
            {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.IMSSEmployerMonthly 0.0}}{{$hasEmployerContributions = true}}{{end}}

            {{if $hasEmployerContributions}}
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">üíº Aportaciones Patronales</div>
                <div class="items-list">
                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.InfonavitEmployerMonthly 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">
                            üè† Infonavit (5%)
                            {{if $pkg.Calculation.HasInfonavitCredit}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">Abono cr√©dito</span>
                            {{else}}
                            <span class="detail-badge">Ahorro</span>
                            {{end}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-value neutral">${{formatFloat (mul $pkg.Calculation.InfonavitEmployerMonthly 12.0) 2}}/a√±o</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}

                    {{if gt $pkg.Calculation.IMSSEmployerMonthly 0.0}}
                    <div class="item">
                        <div class="item-label">üè• IMSS Patronal</div>
                        <div class="item-value neutral">${{formatFloat (mul $pkg.Calculation.IMSSEmployerMonthly 12.0) 2}}/a√±o</div>
                    </div>
                    {{end}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{end}}
        </div>
        {{end}}
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="legal-notice">
            ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Aviso Legal:</strong> Esta herramienta es un simulador de uso exclusivamente informativo y did√°ctico. Los c√°lculos presentados son estimaciones basadas en la legislaci√≥n fiscal vigente (LISR, LSS, RMF 2025) pero no constituyen asesor√≠a fiscal, contable o legal profesional. El desarrollador no se hace responsable por discrepancias con los c√°lculos oficiales del SAT o el IMSS, ni por la toma de decisiones financieras basadas en estos resultados. Se recomienda consultar a un contador p√∫blico certificado para determinaciones fiscales definitivas.
        </div>
        <div class="footer-brand">
            Generado por TotalComp MX ‚Ä¢ totalcomp.mx ‚Ä¢ Versi√≥n 2025
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

